name: Tezpunks
description:
Tezpunks

Year AD 7702, a group of punks are assigned a mysterious mission. These punks are very deadly. They have their own superpowers. Objectives of the mission will be communicated to them from the command center. For now, the only objective communicated to the punks is to time travel to 2021. 

ID #002
Male


Name         : Gulsher
Strength     : 91/100
Intelligence : 78/100

After Gulsher burned the city of Lierra and killed thousands of innocents, he was captured by the army and was sentenced to death. 
He escaped the prison with the help of Balkis and is currently controlling the slaves of Balkis. 
Violent and cruel.
